  <mainDescription>&lt;p> The strategic planning process plays an essential role in forming a company's &#xD;
  strategy. The process results in a strategic business plan or an updated strategic &#xD;
  business plan. A key feature of a strategic business plan is that it outlines &#xD;
  a top-level budget, which establishes the resource allocation map for the coming &#xD;
  period of time (for example,&amp;nbsp;12 to 24 months). The strategic business plan &#xD;
  also sets financial and operating targets. &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p> The content of the strategic business plan can include, but not be limited &#xD;
  to, the following topics: &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &#xD;
  &lt;li> Strategic focus &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Description of the business&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Market analysis&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Marketing plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Products and technologies&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &#xD;
  &lt;li> Research and development organization &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Production and delivery&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Supply chain considerations&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Business systems and processes&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Stakeholder relationships and partner alliances&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Risk factors and regulatory compliance&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Corporate governance&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Financial analysis&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Application of investment funds&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Strategic action plan&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p> These are typical questions that the strategic business plan should answer: &#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What products and services do we deliver?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Where and when do we deliver our products and services?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Which are our primary customer groups?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Where are our primary customers?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What value do our products and services deliver to our customers?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What is our competitive advantage?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &#xD;
  &lt;li> What are our high-priority goals? &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &#xD;
  &lt;li> Which core organizational skills and competencies are vital to achieving &#xD;
    our mission? &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What are our key financial performance indicators?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What are our investment requirements?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        What are our funding resources?&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
  <purpose>&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        To align the management team on&amp;nbsp;the strategic priorities&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &#xD;
  &lt;li> To help determine compensation metrics &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        To provide guidance for financial markets&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ArtifactDescription>
